TEST 0:

*input:

http://127.0.0.1:8080/

*output:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>MAIN PAGE</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color: lightyellow;">
    <h1>Browsing Human and Vertebrates genome</h1>
    <h2>MEDIUM Level Species</h2>
    <p> 1) List of species in the genome database</p>
    <form action="listSpecies" method="get">
      Limit: <input type="text" name="limit">
        <br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="Send">
      <br><br>
</form>
    <p>2) Information about the karyotype</p>
    <form action="karyotype" method="get">
      Select the species: <input type="text" name="specie">
        <br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="Send">
      <br><br>
</form>
    <p>3) Chromosome length </p>
    <form action="chromosomeLength" method="get">
      Select the species: <input type="text" name="specie">
        <br><br>
        Select the chromosome: <input type="text" name="chromo">
        <br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="Send">
      <br><br>
</form>
    <p>4) Sequence of a human gene </p>
    <form action="geneSeq" method="get">
      Introduce the name of the gene: <input type="text" name="gene">
        <br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="Send">
      <br><br>
</form>
<p>5) Information of a human gene </p>
    <form action="geneInfo" method="get">
      Introduce the name of the gene: <input type="text" name="gene">
        <br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="Send">
      <br><br>
</form>
<p>6)  Statistics/Calculation on a human gene </p>
    <form action="geneCalc" method="get">
      Introduce the name of the gene: <input type="text" name="gene">
        <br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="Send">
      <br><br>
</form>
<p>7) List of genes located in chromosome </p>
    <form action="geneList" method="get">
      Introduce the name of the chromosome: <input type="text" name="chromo">
        <br><br>
        Select the start of the gene: <input type="text" name="start">
        <br><br>
        Select the end of the gene: <input type="text" name="end">
        <br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="Send">
      <br><br>
</form>
</body>
</html>
